mod-title = Mod Content Manager
modcontent-title = Manage Content
modcontent-header =
    Tiberian Dawn requires artwork and audio from the original game.

    This content will be automatically loaded if you have the C&C Remastered
    Collection or C&C The Ultimate Collection installed via Steam or the EA app.

    The base game files (without music or videos) can be downloaded from the
    2007 freeware release, and you can provide a copy of the release iso files
    to enable music and videos.

